Google Play gives you access
to a massive [INAUDIBLE]

00:00:21.710 --> 00:00:24.500
of one billion potential users.

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:27.450
Your challenge as a
developer is to [INAUDIBLE]

00:00:27.450 --> 00:00:31.290
the right users, user
