00:07:22.320 --> 00:07:25.679
So the next step is to
interact with your crew

00:07:25.679 --> 00:07:27.970
through the ratings and review
section of the developer

00:07:27.970 --> 00:07:28.840
console.

00:07:28.840 --> 00:07:32.060
It's one of the most important
aspects of the Play Store

00:07:32.060 --> 00:07:37.260
and it's incredibly easy for
you, the developer, to do.

00:07:37.260 --> 00:07:40.920
So ratings are one at the top
ways that users will market

00:07:40.920 --> 00:07:43.210
your app to other people.

00:07:43.210 --> 00:07:46.310
They're are also going to help
you understand what users love

00:07:46.310 --> 00:07:49.440
and hate about your app,
and how their sentiment

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:52.350
has changed over time.

00:07:52.350 --> 00:07:55.230
Replying to reviews is
one of the best ways

00:07:55.230 --> 00:07:58.710
to create meaningful
connections with your users

00:07:58.710 --> 00:08:01.230
and show them that you
listen to their feedback

00:08:01.230 --> 00:08:03.900
to improve your product.

00:08:03.900 --> 00:08:06.820
Now, we listen to you
developers' feedback

00:08:06.820 --> 00:08:09.080
and added some features
that you wanted most

00:08:09.080 --> 00:08:11.230
within the developer console.

00:08:11.230 --> 00:08:12.760
So the ratings
chart that you see

00:08:12.760 --> 00:08:15.210
is now available on
the reviews page,

00:08:15.210 --> 00:08:19.260
making it easy to track trends
and individual star ratings,

00:08:19.260 --> 00:08:22.680
and you can also search
for specific reviews

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:27.150
and do a free text search
across all of your reviews.

00:08:27.150 --> 00:08:29.420
Recently launched,
too, one of the most

00:08:29.420 --> 00:08:31.560
requested features--
being able to get

00:08:31.560 --> 00:08:34.190
a notification
once a user updates

00:08:34.190 --> 00:08:36.549
a review you've responded to.

00:08:39.070 --> 00:08:43.230
Now, ratings can materially
impact your installs.

00:08:43.230 --> 00:08:46.940
So you want to work towards
improving your scores so

00:08:46.940 --> 00:08:49.650
that you could even be
promoted by Google Play.

00:08:49.650 --> 00:08:52.580
We have a minimum bar
of 4.0 for inclusion

00:08:52.580 --> 00:08:55.660
in any of our merchandising
opportunities.

00:08:55.660 --> 00:08:58.450
We encourage everyone
to get into a dialogue

00:08:58.450 --> 00:09:03.230
with your users, replying to
both good and bad reviews.

00:09:03.230 --> 00:09:07.880
It'll make sure there's not
a mutiny on your store page.

00:09:07.880 --> 00:09:11.930
So here's an example from one
of my developers, "ZomboDroid."

00:09:11.930 --> 00:09:14.610
If you ever need an
awesome app to make memes,

00:09:14.610 --> 00:09:17.210
I suggest you check them out.

00:09:17.210 --> 00:09:19.110
But you can see how
they're actively

00:09:19.110 --> 00:09:23.530
responding to low reviews and
asking the user to email them

00:09:23.530 --> 00:09:26.090
at their support address.

00:09:26.090 --> 00:09:27.840
This serves a few purposes.

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:31.520
First, it's going to
help increase engagement.

00:09:31.520 --> 00:09:34.460
Second, it looks much better
to users who've not yet

00:09:34.460 --> 00:09:37.270
downloaded the app, to
show that the developer is

00:09:37.270 --> 00:09:41.110
willing and able to respond
to technical questions

00:09:41.110 --> 00:09:43.190
and support them.

00:09:43.190 --> 00:09:47.280
And again, after you've worked
with the user on their issue,

00:09:47.280 --> 00:09:50.130
going back and asking them
to update their review

00:09:50.130 --> 00:09:53.085
can result in an increase in
your ratings and higher stars.

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:59.330
So, as the song
goes, in the Navy,

00:09:59.330 --> 00:10:01.880
you can sail the seven seas.

00:10:01.880 --> 00:10:04.100
Well, if we're doing
all of that traveling,

00:10:04.100 --> 00:10:05.830
we also need to
make sure that we're

00:10:05.830 --> 00:10:08.850
going to be speaking the right
language for the country whose

00:10:08.850 --> 00:10:10.950
port that we're in.

00:10:10.950 --> 00:10:13.560
Let's continue our
focus on the user

00:10:13.560 --> 00:10:16.000
with a little different
twist, making sure

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:18.680
that they can effectively
interact with your Play Store

00:10:18.680 --> 00:10:21.075
listing and app because
it's in their language.

00:10:23.650 --> 00:10:26.740
So within the developer
console, you already have access

00:10:26.740 --> 00:10:30.540
to a number of optimization
tips and recommendations,

00:10:30.540 --> 00:10:33.600
