You can see these
recommendations bubbled up

00:10:41.630 --> 00:10:45.870
within the to do section
under optimization tips.

00:10:45.870 --> 00:10:47.790
Here you can see
the recommendations

00:10:47.790 --> 00:10:52.320
to translate our store listing,
make the screenshots and videos

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:55.850
reflect our target APK
language, and translate

00:10:55.850 --> 00:10:57.980
the actual strings
within our app.

00:11:01.330 --> 00:11:05.580
So you can easily translate your
Play Store listing page either

00:11:05.580 --> 00:11:08.590
by providing your
own translation text,

00:11:08.590 --> 00:11:11.600
or purchasing professional
translations directly

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:13.850
from the Developer Console.

00:11:13.850 --> 00:11:17.940
If you don't provide translation
text for your store listing,

00:11:17.940 --> 00:11:21.790
Google Play will either show
an automated translation

00:11:21.790 --> 00:11:25.560
or the default language
setting for your application

00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:28.520
but neither of these is
ideal if your users have

00:11:28.520 --> 00:11:29.725
a local language preference.

00:11:32.950 --> 00:11:35.990
In addition to your
Play Store listing page,

00:11:35.990 --> 00:11:37.970
you'll also want to
make sure that your

00:11:37.970 --> 00:11:42.250
APK itself is translated
into other languages.

00:11:42.250 --> 00:11:46.130
Fortunately, Google makes
this extremely easy as well.

00:11:46.130 --> 00:11:48.560
Using the app
translation service,

00:11:48.560 --> 00:11:51.540
you can easily purchase
professional translations

00:11:51.540 --> 00:11:56.800
for your APK strings and
in app items as well.

00:11:56.800 --> 00:12:00.030
To find this option in the
Google Play Developer Console,

00:12:00.030 --> 00:12:02.310
you'll want to sign
in and select an app,

00:12:02.310 --> 00:12:05.880
and then click on
APK on the left side.

00:12:05.880 --> 00:12:09.170
At the bottom, by this APK
Translation Service option,

00:12:09.170 --> 00:12:11.510
you can click Start
or Check Progress

00:12:11.510 --> 00:12:13.560
to launch the Google
Play Translation Manager.

00:12:16.350 --> 00:12:18.170
After you've
selected the language

00:12:18.170 --> 00:12:21.900
that you want to translate
your app or the strings into,

00:12:21.900 --> 00:12:24.570
you can browse a list
of third party vendors

00:12:24.570 --> 00:12:28.770
who are pre-qualified by
Google to offer high quality

00:12:28.770 --> 00:12:30.780
translations.

00:12:30.780 --> 00:12:32.940
You can upload the
strings that you want,

00:12:32.940 --> 00:12:35.870
select the destination
or target language,

00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:40.550
and then choose your translation
vendor based on time and price.

00:12:40.550 --> 00:12:43.160
You can see the estimates that
are given in the Google Play

00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:47.130
Developer Console for each
of these third party options.

00:12:47.130 --> 00:12:49.150
Once you've purchased
translations,

00:12:49.150 --> 00:12:51.550
you'll receive an
email from your vendor

00:12:51.550 --> 00:12:55.040
and can then interact
directly with them

00:12:55.040 --> 00:12:58.350
to work on your translations.

00:12:58.350 --> 00:13:01.840
Once you've added translations
to your apps text strings,

00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:06.100
you can upload the translated
APK file to Google Play

00:13:06.100 --> 00:13:09.180
and translated versions
will be available to users

00:13:09.180 --> 00:13:11.970
whose language preference
matches the translation

00:13:11.970 --> 00:13:15.510
languages that you've added.

00:13:15.510 --> 00:13:19.500
If you stop by later, I actually
have $100 translation service

00:13:19.500 --> 00:13:22.450
coupons that you can pick
up at the tables over here

00:13:22.450 --> 00:13:24.760
after filling out either
our developer profile

00:13:24.760 --> 00:13:26.030
or a review of this session.

00:13:29.060 --> 00:13:32.790
So now you should have a pretty
solid Play Store listing.

00:13:32.790 --> 00:13:34.310
We've talked about
best practices

00:13:34.310 --> 00:13:37.310
for your icon, title,
description, and then

00:13:37.310 --> 00:13:40.010
using store listing
experiments to optimize

00:13:40.010 --> 00:13:41.900
each of those for your users.

