and Beta Testing that
can help you prototype,

00:14:04.930 --> 00:14:09.790
iterate, test, and
launch your app.

00:14:09.790 --> 00:14:12.720
Alpha and Beta testing
is configured directly

00:14:12.720 --> 00:14:14.940
in the Developer Console.

00:14:14.940 --> 00:14:17.850
You have the ability
to upload the APK

00:14:17.850 --> 00:14:21.550
and distribute it before
releasing to the public.

00:14:21.550 --> 00:14:24.990
Users always have to opt
in to this functionality

00:14:24.990 --> 00:14:27.780
