and fix issues.

00:14:41.910 --> 00:14:45.670
There are two ways to share
your Alpha and Beta builds,

00:14:45.670 --> 00:14:48.300
open or closed.

00:14:48.300 --> 00:14:52.740
Closed Alpha or Beta testing
is invite only and managed

00:14:52.740 --> 00:14:54.920
