00:14:54.920 --> 00:14:58.260
This means you'll need to add
email addresses to a group

00:14:58.260 --> 00:15:00.020
and then your users
will have access

00:15:00.020 --> 00:15:03.240
to download the Alpha
and Beta builds.

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:05.300
You can also have
an Open Beta which

00:15:05.300 --> 00:15:09.970
includes a custom URL that
anyone can join and opt into.

00:15:09.970 --> 00:15:12.900
The developer can set a
maximum number of testers

00:15:12.900 --> 00:15:15.560
and the overall progression
might be a Closed Beta

00:15:15.560 --> 00:15:18.460
Test to an Open
Beta Test and then

00:15:18.460 --> 00:15:21.600
actually distributing that
custom URL, via social media,

00:15:21.600 --> 00:15:24.460
to your biggest fans to
get them early access

00:15:24.460 --> 00:15:27.730
and get them testing
out your new app.

00:15:27.730 --> 00:15:30.120
A number of top developers
have seen great success

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:33.720
with Alpha and Beta Testing to
ensure that new releases are

00:15:33.720 --> 00:15:35.210
bug free and successful.

